A simple Serial task including:
- receive transmit true pin changes detection and bit timer
- fifo handling on TX and RX
- possibility to allocate 1bit or 4 bits ports
- possibility to access gpio when 4 bits port used
- possibility to work half-duplx with a single port
- possibility to handle RTS for transmiting on RS485 network
- includes primitives for Infra Red receiver handling
- include XMODEM transmit protocol as a state machine
- include capabilities to listen an asnswer with timeout

original source code on github : https://github.com/fabriceo/XMOS
